title: Ranked match not showin up?
body: Last night around 10, well before the ranked queues were shut down, I won my first promotional game, yet it never showed up in my match history or gave me the win in my series for it.  Decided to wait until today hoping it would show up, the win still isn't showing up.  Anyone else had this problem?

replies.body: They took the ranked queue down for maintenance yesterday?
